<doc id="398928" wikidata="Q961807" url="?curid=398928" title="Villahoz">
<text>Villahoz is a village and municipality in the province of Burgos, Spain. The village is in the wine region known as Ribera del Arlanza, 15 km from Lerma.

==References==
